rows.label: qst103311_msg0001
rows.name:
This person... Don't you
recognize her? Meleph-sama.

rows.label: qst103311_msg0005
rows.name:
Yes... It's rare for a
married couple to both be
senators, so I remembered.

rows.label: qst103311_msg0006
rows.name:
Th-this is terrible. This
is a major incident.

rows.label: qst103311_msg0008
rows.name:
Take the body to military
headquarters and have a
military surgeon examine it.

rows.label: qst103311_msg0012
rows.name:
I'm sorry to ask you to do
something so difficult...

rows.label: qst103311_msg0014
rows.name:
Please don't get used to something
like that, Meleph-sama.

rows.label: qst103311_msg0101
rows.name: I have no idea who this person is.

rows.label: qst103311_msg0102
rows.name:
If someone familiar with the
Superbian Empire or this city
investigated, they might know...

rows.label: qst103311_msg0103
rows.name:
I don't have any leads
right now. We might have
to put this case on hold.
